Bluetongue, Netherlands
-----------------------
Information received on 27 Oct 2008 from Mr Peter W. de Leeuw, Chief
Veterinary Officer, Food Quality and Animal Health, Ministry of
Agriculture, Nature and Food Quality, LA HAYE, Netherlands

Summary
Report type Immediate notification
Start date 10 Sep 2008
Date of first confirmation of the event 24 Oct 2008
Report date 27 Oct 2008
Date submitted to OIE 27 Oct 2008
Reason for notification: New strain of a listed disease
Causal agent Bluetongue virus
Serotype 6
Nature of diagnosis: Clinical, Laboratory (basic), Laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks
